e new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999681677, \"rank\": 3.1866276741953174e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999781865927536, \"rank\": 2.1813872813469654e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal's coach, Carlos Moya, explained toRadioestadio Noche: \\\"It was a setback and we decided that today Rafa would rest and not train to recover.\\\"\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3043825236180818e-11, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Moy\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9999998624716776, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Moya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso